headline: AM Best Affirms Performance Assessment of Delta International Limited’s Affiliates
summary: SINGAPORE, October 31, 2025--AM Best has affirmed the Performance Assessment (assessment) of PA-2 (Excellent) of Delta Insurance New Zealand Limited (New Zealand) and Delta Underwriting Private Limited (Singapore). The companies are assessed on a consolidated basis under their parent, Delta International Limited (Delta). The outlook of the assessment is stable.
